<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBuffer.UnbindMultiSamplingResolveTexture" Title="UnbindMultiSamplingResolveTexture method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IFrameBuffer">IFrameBuffer</PageRef> ->
    UnbindMultiSamplingResolveTexture
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>UnbindMultiSamplingResolveTexture</TypeRef> method unbinds a preiously bound multisample resolve texture.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void UnbindMultiSamplingResolveTexture(AttachmentType type, size_t index = 0);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="AttachmentType" Name="type">
          The attachment type to unbind from multisample resolution.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="size_t" Name="index">
          The attachment index within the specified attachment type.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
